00:38:55,540 --> 00:38:57,020
I had sudden stomach pain last night,

872
00:38:57,020 --> 00:38:58,820
and I think someone poisoned me.

873
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:02,460
That's impossible.

874
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:04,260
Mother, you know me.

875
00:39:04,260 --> 00:39:05,760
I'm always meticulous.

876
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:06,940
There are rarely any mistakes.

877
00:39:06,940 --> 00:39:09,380
Who would dare poison her under my nose?

878
00:39:09,380 --> 00:39:10,700
That's absolutely impossible.

879
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:13,060
Didn't Mr. Zhen

880
00:39:13,060 --> 00:39:14,860
also mention it last night?

881
00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:16,140
Do you all remember?

882
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:18,100
There must be
something fishy about this.

883
00:39:18,100 --> 00:39:19,540
Si is just

884
00:39:19,540 --> 00:39:21,220
following Mr. Zhen's words

885
00:39:21,220 --> 00:39:22,780
and spreading nonsense here.

886
00:39:23,260 --> 00:39:24,100
Aunt Xiao,

887
00:39:24,540 --> 00:39:26,220
when Mr. Zhen said that,

888
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:27,380
my sister wasn't here.

889
00:39:31,140 --> 00:39:31,980
Xiao,

890
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,540
there must be something fishy...

891
00:39:33,540 --> 00:39:34,540
What's with your family?

892
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:35,820
What do you mean?

893
00:39:36,340 --> 00:39:38,420
Why are you targeting me?

894
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:39,860
We were talking about why Si

895
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:41,940
suddenly disappeared.

896
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:43,780
Why does this concern me?

897
00:39:43,780 --> 00:39:45,220
Why not report it to the authorities?

898
00:39:45,220 --> 00:39:47,020
Mr. Zhen can investigate this.

899
00:39:47,540 --> 00:39:49,940
It's a family matter.
No need to report it.

900
00:39:50,140 --> 00:39:51,380
Right.

901
00:39:51,380 --> 00:39:53,580
Si is perfectly fine here.

902
00:39:53,580 --> 00:39:54,660
Why report it?

903
00:39:54,660 --> 00:39:55,660
Mother is right.

904
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:57,820
From now on, our girls

905
00:39:58,220 --> 00:39:59,740
should stay away from generals

906
00:39:59,740 --> 00:40:00,580
like Mr. Yu.

907
00:40:01,900 --> 00:40:03,220
What happened to Qian

908
00:40:03,460 --> 00:40:05,700
is a lesson to us.

909
00:40:06,180 --> 00:40:07,020
Grandmother,

910
00:40:07,220 --> 00:40:08,540
you can't think all generals

911
00:40:08,540 --> 00:40:09,860
are like that.

912
00:40:10,140 --> 00:40:11,500
Does Cao Xingyu's malice

913
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:13,060
mean that all generals

914
00:40:13,060 --> 00:40:14,140
are bad?

915
00:40:14,540 --> 00:40:16,580
If it weren't for generals
defending the borders,

916
00:40:16,640 --> 00:40:18,380
how could we live peacefully?

917
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:20,660
Mother, listen to that.

918
00:40:20,820 --> 00:40:22,260
Is this something

919
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:23,660
a lady should say?

920
00:40:23,740 --> 00:40:26,220
You really have a sharp tongue.

921
00:40:27,340 --> 00:40:29,900
Do you have something going on

922
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:31,420
with him?

923
00:40:31,420 --> 00:40:32,740
Grandmother, of course not.

924
00:40:32,740 --> 00:40:33,580
No?

925
00:40:35,740 --> 00:40:37,180
Fine, then.

926
00:40:38,260 --> 00:40:39,100
Alright.

927
00:40:39,820 --> 00:40:41,540
We've been talking here for a while.

928
00:40:41,540 --> 00:40:42,800
I'm tired. Let's call it a day.

929
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:44,260
Mother, let me help you.

930
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:48,220
