- Mother!

933
00:40:50,700 --> 00:40:52,060
- Mother!
- Get her up!

934
00:40:52,060 --> 00:40:53,820
- Hurry.
- Get up, Mother.

935
00:41:01,620 --> 00:41:02,580
Hurry. Get up.

936
00:41:02,580 --> 00:41:03,660
Come on, Mother.

937
00:41:03,660 --> 00:41:04,820
She's still laughing.

938
00:41:07,340 --> 00:41:08,380
Why did you hit me?

939
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:11,060
Master, you're bad.

940
00:41:11,240 --> 00:41:12,080
How long has it been

941
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:13,140
