- Master, take your clothes off.

947
00:41:24,540 --> 00:41:25,660
Master.

948
00:41:25,740 --> 00:41:27,060
Hurry and stop her!

949
00:41:27,060 --> 00:41:28,340
Master, don't run!

950
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:30,540
Come to my room for fun.

951
00:41:30,540 --> 00:41:31,380
We'll have fun.

952
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:32,380
This...

953
00:41:32,580 --> 00:41:33,660
This is insane.

954
00:41:33,660 --> 00:41:34,980
How shameless!

955
00:41:34,980 --> 00:41:36,340
How improper!

956
00:41:36,500 --> 00:41:37,860
Anmou, listen.

957
00:41:37,860 --> 00:41:39,260
Without my permission,

958
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:41,700
