959
00:41:42,020 --> 00:41:42,860
Yes.

960
00:41:43,260 --> 00:41:44,660
What's going on?

961
00:41:44,660 --> 00:41:45,820
Why has she gone mad?

962
00:41:45,820 --> 00:41:46,660
Grandmother,

963
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:48,340
