964
00:41:48,340 --> 00:41:49,260
Poisoned?

965
00:41:49,260 --> 00:41:50,340
Poisoned...

966
00:41:51,500 --> 00:41:52,740
Didn't your mother

967
00:41:52,740 --> 00:41:54,180
