968
00:41:54,380 --> 00:41:55,460
No one would be poisoned

969
00:41:55,940 --> 00:41:58,100
in this household.

970
00:41:58,100 --> 00:42:00,340
Right. Aunt Xiao runs a tight ship.

971
00:42:00,500 --> 00:42:02,220
There wouldn't be such a mistake.

972
00:42:02,940 --> 00:42:05,660
Looks like Xiao can't manage

973
00:42:06,460 --> 00:42:08,060
