984
00:42:34,100 --> 00:42:35,020
(No.)

985
00:42:42,100 --> 00:42:42,940
Grandmother,

986
00:42:43,060 --> 00:42:45,140
I think Si is the perfect choice.

987
00:42:51,900 --> 00:42:52,740
Mother,

988
00:42:53,060 --> 00:42:54,780
Si is still young...

989
00:43:00,540 --> 00:43:01,980
Then it's settled.

